31:27.037 --> 31:28.107
Caleb.

31:28.238 --> 31:30.582
So you want to
skate or what?

31:30.707 --> 31:33.347
No, man, I kind of
just wanted to be...

31:33.476 --> 31:34.921
To be alone?

31:35.045 --> 31:35.716
I know how
that goes,

31:35.845 --> 31:37.449
I know how
you feel.

31:37.581 --> 31:38.389
Oh you
think so?

31:38.515 --> 31:39.653
Yeah.

31:39.783 --> 31:41.319
Been to plenty of spots just
like this back home.

31:41.451 --> 31:42.589
I go skate there
all the time.

31:42.719 --> 31:47.361
All by myself,
all alone.

31:47.490 --> 31:48.332
Where's home?

31:48.458 --> 31:49.960
Liverpool,
back in England.

31:50.093 --> 31:51.333
You know when I was
going through some stuff,

31:51.461 --> 31:53.236
the challenges of life,
the things that

31:53.363 --> 31:57.334
I tried to drink away or party
away or smoke away perhaps,

31:57.467 --> 32:01.643
but that never
really helped.

32:01.771 --> 32:03.341
Well then
what helps?

32:08.912 --> 32:09.720
Take it
easy, man.

32:09.846 --> 32:11.154
Good talking
to you Caleb.

32:16.486 --> 32:18.864
Yo.

32:18.989 --> 32:20.366
Thought you
wanted to skate?

32:20.490 --> 32:23.664
Thought you wanted
to be alone?

32:23.960 --> 32:26.372
Grab your board, let's go,
let's go skate.

35:33.483 --> 35:38.193
Your father will not
forgive your sins.

35:47.397 --> 35:49.035
Dear Caleb,

35:49.165 --> 35:51.008
If you are
reading this,

35:51.134 --> 35:54.604
my prayers have
been answered.

35:54.737 --> 35:56.546
I know growing up
without a father

35:56.673 --> 35:58.949
has been very
hard for you

35:59.242 --> 36:02.587
and I know I haven't
always been the best mother.

36:02.712 --> 36:07.161
But I've always tried to do
what I thought was best for you.

36:07.283 --> 36:09.456
I love you
so much,

36:09.586 --> 36:11.065
that I thought if I
made you believe

36:11.187 --> 36:15.966
that your father and
I were a one time encounter

36:16.092 --> 36:18.766
that you would
hurt less.

36:18.895 --> 36:21.637
I know now that I was
wrong for that,

36:21.764 --> 36:23.744
and I'm very sorry.

36:23.867 --> 36:26.643
The truth is, that
I loved your father,

36:26.769 --> 36:28.715
and I still do,

36:28.838 --> 36:32.183
and you were created
from that love.

36:32.308 --> 36:33.514
So I hope you
can find it

36:33.643 --> 36:36.453
in your heart
some day to forgive me.

36:36.579 --> 36:37.922
I love you.

36:38.214 --> 36:40.285
Mom.

36:56.432 --> 36:57.536
Caleb?

36:59.769 --> 37:01.840
Hey Ralf.

37:03.907 --> 37:05.853
Why do you
do this?

37:05.975 --> 37:07.955
Do what?

37:08.077 --> 37:08.714
This, why do you,

37:08.845 --> 37:10.825
why do you live
like this?

37:14.117 --> 37:18.623
It enables me to spread
the word of God.

37:18.755 --> 37:23.329
What about
your family?

37:23.459 --> 37:26.804
It was Easter
Sunday.

37:26.930 --> 37:29.240
Me and my wife and
my daughter were going

37:29.365 --> 37:32.539
