my mother in law for Easter.

37:32.669 --> 37:34.410
Do you like my
dress, daddy?

37:34.537 --> 37:35.777
It's beautiful,
sweetheart.

37:35.905 --> 37:37.509
Are we ready to
go to grandma's?

37:37.640 --> 37:39.142
Yeah!

37:39.275 --> 37:40.549
It's my
secretary,

37:40.677 --> 37:42.520
she wouldn't page me unless
it was really important.

37:42.645 --> 37:47.151
Honey, you promised no
work till we get back.

37:47.283 --> 37:50.730
My secretary
called and

37:50.853 --> 37:52.298
I forgot to sign
off on a case

37:52.422 --> 37:54.629
that had to be postmarked
the next day.

37:54.757 --> 37:57.636
I had to go to
the office.

37:57.760 --> 38:00.263
So I sent my wife and my
daughter to go ahead.

38:04.901 --> 38:09.043
They never
made it.

38:09.172 --> 38:12.153
Drunk driver
crossed the line.

38:12.275 --> 38:16.690
Hit 'em
head on.

38:16.813 --> 38:19.419
I should have
been driving.

38:27.957 --> 38:30.267
My daughter would be
twenty-two today.

38:35.031 --> 38:39.605
After that I
just gave up.

38:39.736 --> 38:40.646
I couldn't accept
the fact

38:40.770 --> 38:44.217
that I'd never
see them again.

38:44.340 --> 38:47.378
Never hold my wife or
hear my daughter say

38:47.510 --> 38:52.357
Daddy, I
love you.

38:52.482 --> 38:54.792
Sol crawled into
a bottle and took

38:54.917 --> 38:57.864
whatever pills I could
get my hands on,

39:01.024 --> 39:04.528
What happened to
the driver?

39:04.661 --> 39:09.337
He got three years
for manslaughter.

39:09.465 --> 39:12.412
I hated that man more than
anything else in the world.

39:14.737 --> 39:16.307
I wished every day
that the same thing

39:16.439 --> 39:18.510
would happen to
his family.

39:21.544 --> 39:24.218
Till one day,

39:24.347 --> 39:27.328
I realized that
all that hate

39:27.450 --> 39:31.330
was never going to
bring 'em back.

39:31.454 --> 39:33.832
And it was slowly
killing me.

39:36.492 --> 39:39.905
So what'd
you do?

39:40.196 --> 39:42.301
I forgave him.

39:45.034 --> 39:47.605
It's time for you to
forgive yourself.

40:18.668 --> 40:19.612
Sup?

40:23.873 --> 40:28.015
I'm really sorry
about your mom.

40:28.144 --> 40:30.522
