something, man.

40:43.760 --> 40:45.137
Why?

40:45.261 --> 40:46.934
What's the point
of it?

40:47.063 --> 40:49.703
Well he keeps...

40:49.832 --> 40:51.778
Saying...

40:51.901 --> 40:53.744
What?

40:53.870 --> 40:55.781
What happened
to your lip?

40:59.275 --> 41:01.221
Did Ryder
do that?

41:05.848 --> 41:07.794
Man this has
got to stop.

41:11.687 --> 41:13.257
Tell Ryder
I'm in.

41:13.389 --> 41:16.063
But we do
it my way.

41:16.192 --> 41:20.504
The skate
park.

41:20.630 --> 41:22.769
Sorry.

41:31.240 --> 41:34.710
Big day,
Jack.

41:34.844 --> 41:37.415
You alright?

41:37.547 --> 41:38.457
Huh?

41:38.581 --> 41:41.653
