it's not--

41:48.257 --> 41:49.861
No, not concerned,
not concerned at all.

41:49.992 --> 41:52.097
In fact I think your plan
is just great.

41:52.228 --> 41:53.104
Great.

41:53.229 --> 41:55.266
You know,

41:55.398 --> 41:59.039
