was more important

42:03.139 --> 42:05.210
than his job.

42:05.341 --> 42:06.649
And I could never
seem to wrap

42:06.776 --> 42:10.485
my mind around
that until today.

42:10.613 --> 42:14.390
So I would like
to thank you.

42:14.517 --> 42:16.929
For accepting
my apology,

42:17.053 --> 42:21.331
